<plot>Kong is a warrior by necessity, fighting for sustenance and struggling to keep her grasp on the world of the living in a desert wasteland hell. After barricading herself inside an abandoned home for protection, a maimed and bloody body she's trapped herself with returns to life and speaks of one thing: Eating her alive. 'Son Of Golem' is an absurdist take on the pressures of cultural assimilation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?506512</url></doc>
